## FLURM VM Arguments for Migration Testing

## Node name
-name ${FLURM_NODE_NAME:-flurm@localhost}

## Cookie for distribution
-setcookie ${FLURM_COOKIE:-flurm_migration_test}

## Heartbeat
-heart

## Enable SMP
-smp auto

## Async threads
+A 30

## Max ports
+Q 65536

## Max processes
+P 1048576

## Kernel options
-kernel inet_dist_listen_min 9100
-kernel inet_dist_listen_max 9105

## Logger config
-kernel logger_level info

## Shell history
-kernel shell_history enabled
